rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2603b663776e3b9780bdf440d0e34c621d2dcf3e","tid":956891,"uid":21654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:49:39.000Z","msg":"入屋第一時間同佢建立關係，一有時間就遠少少距離同佢眼神接觸，慢慢眨眼，同貓溝通方式，代表我愛你<br />\n除左餵食清沙盆，唔好近距離攪佢，環境唔好嘈，直到佢都對你眨眼就成功<br />\n<br />\n你而家無籠就好難同佢有眼神交流，好難建立互信關係"},{"pid":"e99af855bba37a06290dd182248d52b4d19487bc","tid":956891,"uid":122680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"留名，我最近都有新貓女入屋，肯俾摸，但一望佢就胡胡聲縮後...<br />\n<br />\n家有兩主子仔，一老餅，一隻2歲，2歲果隻對新貓又fee又胡<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0w6odjN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0w6odjN.png&h=511c0c5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ce7384446bb4908abc2cd6d38655f482ba6712b","tid":956891,"uid":61554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"留名 <br />\n新貓入屋困籠幾耐就喵足幾耐<br />\n一放佢出黎舊貓就咬佢頸 格住籠都會伸手入去打新貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bb41e293033127364742eb47bad44c915e4caa","tid":956891,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T00:20:33.000Z","msg":"你新貓係邊領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}